<plot>Vick, a 24 year old suburbanite, tells his friends how he is a ladies man. The catch is that Vick's ladies tend to be minors whom he meets at high school functions. Over a game a Risk, Vick argues his lifestyle and soon unveils his method and strategy while on a date with these girls. Vick plays his game of Risk as he tells his friends of his game of Risk. Does Vick love living on the edge and how far is too far before he is pushed too far and he plummets to his demise?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?201435</url></doc>
